window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Inferno, noun.</p> <ol> <li>A large fire that is dangerously out of control</li> <li>A place of suffering; hell</li> </ol> <p>Tessa is a school teacher and single mom starting a new life in Paris, Tennessee. Romance is the last thing on her mind.</p> <p>Bishop is the leader of the Devil Chasers' Motorcycle Club and a single dad trying to rescue his son from the sins of his father. He doesn't have time to add a woman into the mix.</p> <p>Bishop's past won't let go, and soon Tessa is swept up in the powerful, intense biker's world - and all the danger that brings. When all hell breaks loose, will their love survive the blast, or will everything be lost in the inferno?</p>"; 
